<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CASE STUDY: DIGITAL ADVERTISING GROWTH</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html {
    width: 100%;
    background: white;
  }

  body {
    width: 210mm;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: white;
  }

  /* Centered wrapper — 160mm content width centered in 210mm page */
  .page {
    width: 210mm;
    min-height: 297mm;
    background: white;
    padding: 28px 25mm; /* 25mm left + right = 160mm content */
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #111827;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding-bottom:14px; margin-bottom:22px; border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb; }
  .brand-name { font-size:13px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:0.12em; color:#ea580c; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .brand-tag { font-size:7.5px; color:#9ca3af; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.08em; margin-top:2px; }

  /* HERO */
  .badge { display:inline-block; background:#fceae1; color:#ea580c; font-size:7.5px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:3px 9px; border-radius:4px; margin-bottom:9px; }
  .hero { margin-bottom:20px; }
  h1 { font-size:24px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.15; color:#111827; margin-bottom:7px; }
  .hero-sub { font-size:9px; color:#6b7280; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .hero-meta { font-size:8px; color:#9ca3af; }

  /* STATS */
  .stats { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:10px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .stat { background:#f9fafb; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px; padding:13px 11px; }
  .sv { font-size:20px; font-weight:800; line-height:1; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .sl { font-size:7.5px; font-weight:700; color:#374151; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.08em; margin-bottom:2px; }
  .ss { font-size:7.5px; color:#9ca3af; }

  /* STRATEGY + TARGETING (always 2 columns, equal width) */
  .two-col { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; }

  .strategy { background:#111827; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; color:white; }
  .strat-title { font-size:10.5px; font-weight:700; color:#ea580c; margin-bottom:7px; }
  .strat-body { font-size:8.5px; color:#d1d5db; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:11px; }
  .segs { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:7px; }
  .seg { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius:6px; padding:9px; }
  .sp { font-size:14px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:2px; }
  .st { font-size:7.5px; font-weight:700; color:white; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:3px; }
  .sd { font-size:7.5px; color:#9ca3af; line-height:1.5; }

  .targeting { background:#f9fafb; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; }
  .tgt-title { font-size:10.5px; font-weight:700; color:#111827; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .ti { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin-bottom:7px; font-size:9px; color:#374151; }
  .td { width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; flex-shrink:0; }
  .infra-label { font-size:8px; font-weight:700; color:#374151; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-top:10px; padding-top:8px; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .ii { font-size:8px; color:#6b7280; margin-bottom:3px; padding-left:8px; }

  /* EMAIL VARIATIONS — full width 2-col grid */
  .email-grid { display:grid; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .ebox { border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px; padding:14px; }
  .el { font-size:7.5px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; margin-bottom:7px; }
  .ebody { background:#f9fafb; border-radius:6px; padding:10px; }

  /* QUOTE — full width */
  .quote-block { padding:14px 18px; background:#f9fafb; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .qt { font-size:9.5px; font-style:italic; color:#374151; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .qa { font-size:8.5px; font-weight:700; }
  .qc { font-size:7.5px; color:#9ca3af; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta { background:#111827; border-radius:10px; padding:20px; text-align:center; margin-top:14px; }
  .cta h2 { font-size:17px; font-weight:800; color:white; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .cta-sub { font-size:8.5px; color:#9ca3af; line-height:1.5; margin-bottom:11px; }
  .btn-fill { display:inline-block; background:#ea580c; color:white; font-size:8.5px; font-weight:700; padding:7px 18px; border-radius:6px; margin-right:7px; text-decoration:none; }
  .btn-out { display:inline-block; border:1px solid #4b5563; color:#d1d5db; font-size:8.5px; font-weight:600; padding:7px 18px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none; }
  .guarantees { font-size:7.5px; color:#6b7280; margin-top:9px; }
  .guarantees span { margin:0 7px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="header">
    <div>
      <div class="brand-name">ASCENDLY</div>
      <div class="brand-tag">Lead Gen Experts</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:#000000;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;height:52px;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="max-height:38px;max-width:160px;width:auto;display:block;" /></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge">CASE STUDY: DIGITAL ADVERTISING GROWTH</div>
    <h1>Filling the calendar for Nett Solutions.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">How we helped an established Orange County digital marketing and ad services agency build a consistent outbound pipeline targeting small and mid-size business owners.</p>
    <p class="hero-meta">2025 - 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; nettsolutions.com</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats"><div class="stat"><div class="sv" style="color:#ea580c">35+</div><div class="sl">QUALIFIED MEETINGS</div><div class="ss">SMB decision-makers</div></div><div class="stat"><div class="sv" style="color:#ea580c">19%</div><div class="sl">CLOSE RATE</div><div class="ss">Outbound to signed client</div></div><div class="stat"><div class="sv" style="color:#ea580c">$1.5k-$5k</div><div class="sl">AVG. MONTHLY RETAINER</div><div class="ss">Per new client</div></div><div class="stat"><div class="sv" style="color:#ea580c">4</div><div class="sl">SERVICE LINES</div><div class="ss">SEO, PPC, Social, Yelp</div></div></div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="strategy">
      <div class="strat-title">&#9889; The Campaign Approach</div>
      <div class="strat-body">Nett Solutions relied heavily on referrals and organic search. We built targeted sequences that spoke directly to small business owners frustrated with ad spend that was not producing clear ROI.</div>
      <div class="segs"><div class="seg"><div class="sp" style="color:#ea580c">50%</div><div class="st">LOCAL SERVICE BUSINESSES</div><div class="sd">Restaurants, contractors, and service providers spending on ads without clear ROI.</div></div><div class="seg"><div class="sp" style="color:#ea580c">50%</div><div class="st">E-COMMERCE AND RETAIL</div><div class="sd">Online stores looking for performance-based search and social campaigns.</div></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="targeting">
      <div class="tgt-title">&#128203; The Targeting</div>
      <div class="ti"><div class="td" style="background:#ea580c"></div><span>Small Business Owners</span></div><div class="ti"><div class="td" style="background:#ea580c"></div><span>Marketing Managers at SMBs</span></div><div class="ti"><div class="td" style="background:#ea580c"></div><span>Companies with $3k+ monthly ad spend</span></div>
      <div class="infra-label">Infrastructure</div>
      <div class="ii">• 25+ Domains</div><div class="ii">• 100+ Sending Accounts</div><div class="ii">• Google and Microsoft inbox split</div><div class="ii">• Weekly deliverability monitoring</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
